code: // -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- /**  * Checks, if this enum constant represents in fact an order. That is,  * whether this property is not equal to <tt>Order.NONE</tt>.  *  * @return True, if this enum constant is unequal to <tt>Order.NONE</tt>,  *         false otherwise.  */ public boolean isOrdered() {     return this != Order.NONE. }
public String getShortName() {     return this == ASCENDING ? "ASC" : this == DESCENDING ? "DESC" : this == ANY ? "*" : "-". }
